(106, 1, '2015-09-16 16:04:47', '2015-09-16 16:04:47', '<h3><em>A plan for all seasons</em></h3>\r\nBridgeland does not take the label “<strong>master planned community</strong>” lightly. In fact, developers created a road map for the evolution of Bridgeland very early in the community’s history. This blueprint is a multi-layered approach for the placement of residential neighborhoods, a hierarchy of parks and amenities, as well as public and private schools. Additionally, a detailed preservation plan outlines the community’s environmentally conscious approaches to irrigation, energy and wildlife.\r\n<p dir="ltr"><a href="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/why-bridgeland/thoughtfully-planned/master-environmental-plan/">Master Environmental Plan</a>\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/why-bridgeland/thoughtfully-planned/master-parks-plan/">Master Parks Plan</a>\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/why-bridgeland/thoughtfully-planned/master-educational-plan/">Master Education Plan</a></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-217" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/mallard-Lake-2.jpg" alt="mallard Lake 2" width="1024" height="683" /></p>', 'Thoughtfully Planned', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'thoughtfully-planned', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:36:58', '2015-09-21 15:36:58', '', 76, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=106', 4, 'page', '', 0),
