(121, 1, '2015-09-16 16:20:47', '2015-09-16 16:20:47', '<h3><i>Top-rated Homebuilders</i></h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Bridgeland is proud to offer products from some of the most well-respected builders in the Houston real estate industry. Homes range in price, style and density, creating an architecturally-interesting and diverse community aesthetic.  Price points begin in the $250s and exceed $1 million.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><em>Hidden Creek</em></h3>\r\n<h4>Homes in Cryer Creek from the $300s</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.ryland.com/find-your-new-home/11-houston/6311-bridgeland.html" target="_blank">Ryland Homes</a>: (832) 863-7393</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.beazer.com/houston-TX/bridgeland-hidden-creek---55" target="_blank">Beazer Homes</a>: (281) 206-2645</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">Homes in Larrison Creek from the $360s</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.coventryhomes.com/houston/bridgelandhiddencreek">Coventry Homes</a> – (713) 260-4180</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Homes in Beech Creek from the $380s</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/Find-Your-Home/Houston/Bridgeland/Bridgeland-55" target="_blank">Perry Homes</a>: (281) 373-0920</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Homes in Noelke Creek from the $350s</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://westin-homes.com/subdivision/bridgeland-sec-6-11/" target="_blank">Westin Homes</a>: (281) 657-7480</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.meritagehomes.com/search/houston-tx/bridgeland-hidden-creek/#.VPClu_nF9Z0" target="_blank">Meritage Homes</a>: (713) 791-8333</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Homes in Rosita Creek from the $410s</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.lennar.com/New-Homes/Texas/Houston/Cypress/Bridgeland/Classic-and-Wentworth-Collections" target="_blank">Village Builders</a>: (281) 746-3051</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.taylormorrison.com/new-homes/texas/houston/cypress/bridgeland-community" target="_blank">Taylor Morrison</a>: (832) 606-8538</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Homes in Chacon Creek from the $500s</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/Find-Your-Home/Houston/Bridgeland/Bridgeland-70" target="_blank">Perry Homes</a>: (281) 304-0610</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Homes in Hickory Creek from the $540s</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.darlinghomes.com/new-homes/texas/houston/cypress/bridgeland-hidden-creek-community" target="_blank">Darling Homes</a>: (713) 385-7742</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">Homes in Hidden Creek Estates from the $710s</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="https://www.perryhomes.com/Find-Your-Home/Houston/Bridgeland/Bridgeland-100">Perry Homes</a> – (281) 304-0610</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr"></h4>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr"><em>Lakeland Heights</em></h3>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">From the $260s</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.jkylehomes.com/lakeland-heights-bridgeland/" target="_blank">J. Kyle Homes</a>: (281) 304-9400</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.davidweekleyhomes.com/new-homes/tx/houston/cypress/lakeland-heights-50" target="_blank">David Weekley Homes</a>: (281) 249-7757</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">From the $230s (Townhome Series)</h4>\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/Find-Your-Home/Houston/Bridgeland/Bridgeland---Townhomes-of-Lakeland-Heights" target="_blank">Perry Homes</a>: (281) 373-0920</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-241" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Builder_web-version.jpg" alt="Builder_web version" width="960" height="720" />', 'Builders', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'builders', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:43:48', '2015-09-21 15:43:48', '', 117, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=121', 1, 'page', '', 0),
