(127, 1, '2015-09-16 16:21:56', '2015-09-16 16:21:56', 'Connectivity and convenience play an important role in the planning of Bridgeland. There will be four distinct villages within the community, defining the land plan and offering residents easy walking and biking access to parks and trails, playgrounds, pool complexes, schools, employment, worship and shopping.\r\n\r\nEach village offers a wide range of housing prices, styles and densities, from conventional neighborhoods to custom home designs in excess of $1 million. Lakeland Village is the first of four villages to open in Bridgeland, to be followed by Parkland Village, Prairieland Village and Creekland Village as development continues.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-277" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/LLH_1.jpg" alt="LLH_1" width="1024" height="683" />', 'Village Life', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'village-life', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:47:01', '2015-09-21 15:47:01', '', 117, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=127', 4, 'page', '', 0),
