(144, 1, '2015-09-16 16:43:32', '2015-09-16 16:43:32', '<em><strong>Bridgeland Welcome Center</strong></em>\r\n\r\n16919 N. Bridgeland Lake Pkwy.\r\nCypress, TX 77433\r\n(281) 304-5588 or (866) 232-0270\r\n<a href="mailto:welcomecenter@bridgeland.com">welcomecenter@bridgeland.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>From US 290 (the Northwest Freeway)</em></strong>\r\n\r\nTraveling northwest on US 290 outbound from Houston, take the Spring-Cypress/Cypress-Rosehill/Fry Road exit. Turn left on Fry Road (2nd traffic light). Proceed south on Fry Road for approximately 2. 5 miles. Turn right on North Bridgleand Lake Parkway, the main entrance to Bridgeland.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>From SH 99 (the Grand Parkway)</em></strong>\r\n\r\nComing south from the Grand Parkway, exit Bridgeland Creek Parkway and turn right at the light. If coming north from I-10, exit the Grand Parkway at Bridgeland Creek Parkway and turn left. Remain straight on House Hahl/ Hidden Pass until taking a left on East Creekside Bend. Follow along until turning left at Josey Ranch Road. The entrance to the Welcome Center will be ahead on the right.\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id="338" title="Contact Us"]', 'Contact Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-us', '', '', '2015-09-21 17:27:30', '2015-09-21 17:27:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=144', 4, 'page', '', 0),
