(154, 1, '2015-09-16 19:13:16', '2015-09-16 19:13:16', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Blog', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-16 19:13:16', '2015-09-16 19:13:16', '', 2, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(155, 1, '2015-09-16 19:36:50', '2015-09-16 19:36:50', 'With a range from traditional-styles in Lakeland Heights to custom-built designs in Hidden Creek, buyers are sure to find a variety of homes in Bridgeland that fit their various tastes and specific needs.\r\n\r\nHidden Creek will host 1,000 home sites, a 20-acre park, 142 acres of lakes and homes built by <a href="http://www.beazer.com/houston-TX/bridgeland-hidden-creek---55" target="_blank">Beazer Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.darlinghomes.com/new-homes/texas/houston/cypress/bridgeland-hidden-creek-community" target="_blank">Darling Homes</a>,<a href="http://www.meritagehomes.com/search/houston-tx/bridgeland-hidden-creek/" target="_blank">Meritage Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/find-your-home/houston/bridgeland.aspx" target="_blank">Perry Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.ryland.com/find-your-new-home/11-houston/6311-bridgeland.html" target="_blank">Ryland Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.taylormorrison.com/new-homes/texas/houston/cypress/bridgeland-community" target="_blank">Taylor Morrison Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.lennar.com/New-Homes/Texas/Houston/Cypress/Bridgeland/Classic-and-Wentworth-Collections" target="_blank">Village Builders</a> and <a href="http://westin-homes.com/communities/details/6065" target="_blank">Westin Homes</a>. Homes in this area start at $300,000 and can exceed $1 million.\r\n\r\nLakeland Heights'' price range is from the $250s to $300s. Homes are built by <a href="http://www.davidweekleyhomes.com/new-homes/tx/houston/cypress/lakeland-heights-50" target="_blank">David Weekley Homes</a>, <a href="http://www.jkylehomes.com/lakeland-heights-bridgeland/" target="_blank">J. Kyle Homes</a> and <a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/Find-Your-Home/Houston/Bridgeland/Bridgeland---Townhomes-of-Lakeland-Heights" target="_blank">Perry Homes</a>. The community also provides walking-distance access to local schools, Lakeland Activity Center and the future Lakeland Village Center.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-245 size-full" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/UrbanNights_370_1.jpg" alt="UrbanNights_370_1" width="1024" height="700" />', 'Current Communities', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'current-communities', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:44:48', '2015-09-21 15:44:48', '', 123, 'http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/?page_id=155', 0, 'page', '', 0),
