 fun-filled stage performances</li>\n	<li>Roaming entertainment</li>\n	<li>Kids'' area sponsored by <a href="http://fry.foundrychurch.org/home.cfm">The Foundry</a></li>\n	<li>Pumkin patch and farmers market</li>\n	<li>Pet product and service exhibitors</li>\n	<li>Dog resuce groups</li>\n	<li>Food truck area</li>\n	<li>Pumpkin decorating</li>\n	<li>Photo-op area</li>\n	<li>Sand art</li>\n	<li>Face painting and balloon artist</li>\n	<li>Dock diving with <a href="http://www.splashdogs.com/" target="_blank">Splash Dogs</a></li>\n	<li>Performance from <a href="http://www.houstonfrisbeedogs.com/" target="_blank">Houston Canine Frisbee Disc Club</a></li>\n	<li>Doggie fashion show emceed by <a href="https://www.facebook.com/meteorologistcaseycurry?fref=ts" target="_blank">Casey Curry</a></li>\n</ul>\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-359" src="http://localhost:8888/Bridgeland/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/House-Cats-Act-31.jpg" alt="House Cats Act 31" width="750" height="499" />\n\n[/su_tab]\n\n[su_tab title="exhibitors"]\n<h3>Exhibitors</h3>\n<ul>\n	<li><a href="http://blackhorseah.com/">Blackhorse Animal Hospital</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://cypresslakesanimal.com/">Cypress Lakes Animal Hospital</a></li>\n	<li>Tinaquero, LLC</li>\n	<li><a href="http://www.realestatewithamy.com/">The Lippincott Team - Better Homes and Garden / Gary Greene</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://www.superdave.com/home.php"> Flory Team</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://www.houstonswimclub.com/">Houston Swim Club</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://www.memorialhermann.org/">Memorial Hermann Cypress</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://cyfairanimalhospital.com/">Cy-Fair Animal Hospital</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://naturalpawz.com/">Natural Pawz</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://www.doodycalls.com/">Doody Calls</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.libertymutual.com/andreashotwell">Liberty Mutual</a></li>\n	<li><a href="http://www.charlesdyeriv.com/">Charles E. Dyer IV, DDS</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.face